<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Blog by Alex Jiang]]></title><description><![CDATA[a personal blog built by Gatsby]]></description><link>https://alexxyjiang.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Jul 2021 09:43:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[Deal with Linux Files via inode]]></title><description><![CDATA[deal with linux file with inode is an important alternative.]]></description><link>https://alexxyjiang.github.io/posts/deal-with-linux-files-via-inode</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://alexxyjiang.github.io/posts/deal-with-linux-files-via-inode</guid><pubDate>Fri, 30 Mar 2012 17:35:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
